HEADWORD: Nasofrontal
<hw>Na`so*fron"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Naso-</ets> + <ets>frontal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to the nose and the front of the head; <as>as, the
embryonic <ex>nasofrontal</ex> process which forms the anterior boundary
of the mouth</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

